change swap file size
/etc/dphys-swapfile

hdmi sleep
add line to /boot/config.txt
hdmi_blanking=1

using Korean
install font
sudo apt-get install fonts-lexi-gulim

sudo apt-get install ibus
sudo apt-get install ibus-hangul
